                  <acquisition>
                     <p>
                        <name type="person">Moses Gaster</name> (b. 1856, d. 1939), scholar and rabbi: his
                manuscript, Cod. G. 75: inscribed with his name on fols. 2r, 322r (stamped);
                purchased by the British Museum from him on 12 April, 1924: inscribed on back
                flyleaf (i)v; date of accession 2 August 1927: inscribed on fol. 322v.
                     </p>
                  </acquisition>
               </history>
